Located in Bangrak, Samui Backpacker Hotel is a 1-minute walk from a pier that can take guests to Ko Phangan and the famous full moon parties. It offers dormitory-style and private rooms with free WiFi.

The hotel is a 5-minute walk from Koh Tao Pier. It is 1.9 mi from Samui Airport.

Rooms are fitted with air-conditioning. Private rooms feature internal bathroom, while shared bathrooms are available for guests of the dormitory rooms.

Guests can enjoy local dishes and drinks at the on-site restaurant.

The property features a tour desk, shuttle service and laundry service. Free private parking is possible on site. For those looking for a relaxing afternoon at the outdoor pool. Guests can also participate in daily pool volleyball and water polo games with the other travelers.

Couples in particular like the location – they rated it 8.0 for a two-person trip.

The fine print
